      </p>
      <p>
        You may print or download such material in electronic form on your
        local hard drive for your personal and non-commercial use.
      </p>
      <p>
        You may not alter or otherwise make any changes to any material that
        you print or download including, without limitation, removing any
        copyright or proprietary notices.
      </p>
      <p>
